# This directory holds your datasets.
#
# Recommended structure:
#
#   data/
#   ├── IXI-T1/                    ← Raw IXI T1 NIfTI files
#   │   ├── IXI002-Guys-0828-T1.nii.gz
#   │   ├── IXI012-HH-1211-T1.nii.gz
#   │   └── ...
#   │
#   ├── IXI-T1-preprocessed/       ← (Optional) Preprocessed volumes
#   │   └── ...
#   │
#   └── other-dataset/             ← Add more datasets as needed
#
# Download IXI T1 data:
#   https://brain-development.org/ixi-dataset/
#   → Click "IXI-T1" to download the tar archive
#   → Extract: tar -xf IXI-T1.tar -C data/IXI-T1/
#
# This directory is git-ignored. Only this .gitkeep file is tracked.
